data.description: REDUCED $ 5000. Shows Beautifully, Well Maintained. Newer CHA Heat Pump 2021! Priced to Sell! Furnishings available as well. Only 1 Mile to Indian Rocks Beach for Scenic Walks ,Gulf Breezes & Sunsets. Also enjoy the Beach Nightlife, Waterfront Dining & Pubs & Music on the Beautiful Gulf of Mexico & Intracoastal Waterways.  Enjoy the convenience of this location minutes away to your local Publix, Neighborhood Walmart , Professional Offices, Shops & Restaurants. Directly steps behind Building Two is one of three Community pools to enjoy. Two Nature Parks are also nearby with walking trails, picnic pavilions & exhibits. The Laundry facility on each floor has new washer & dryers, just steps away.  Building 2 comprised of Only Nine Units each floor.   Building 2 has ample parking. Other benefits within the community include Shuffleboard Courts, Grilling Areas, The Lakehouse Clubhouse has Vibrant Activities Year around, Library, Pool Table, Kitchen for Parties, an Outside Waterfront Deck with tables & chairs for Relaxation.   Medical facilities are nearby too. The open floor plan has a spacious living room dining area combination, split bedroom plan too. Beautiful Florida Room overlooking Landscaped Grounds & your own Serene Privacy.  Three Community Swimming Pools include the Clubhouse heated pool with an adjacent hot tub. The Landscaped Grounds are quite spacious, spanning approximately 16 acres with Beautiful Ponds & Fountains. Actually a Hidden Treasure Community near One of Finest Florida Beaches! This is Truly a Wonderful Location for Enjoyable Florida Living at its Finest. NO Flood Insurance required.
